						               													<description>Z-Game 2 is a competitive strategy game for 2-4 players who accumulate resources, recruit mercenaries, destroy the last strongholds of civilization, fulfill missions and fight with zombies.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Try to survive in post-apocalyptic world! On their turn, the player moves around the city tiles, destroy them, enters into battles with other players and zombies by playing cards from the hand - all in order to fulfill the current goal of the round.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the beginning of each round, a new event card is opened. If this is the 8th card, you will play the final round.&amp;#10;Then update the goals of the round. In each round, goals are different, so players will always have something to do.&amp;#10;After this setup of the round, players perform their turns which include three phases: 1. moving, 2. fighting, if they meet with enemies, and 3. getting resources from occupied territories and feeding crew.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game also ends if one player has completed eight or more goals.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The winner is the player who accomplished most of the goals. If there is a tie here, then the winner is the one who has more people left in the city. If there is a tie here, arrange an arm wrestling - in the post-apocalypse there is always only one winner!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game boasts simple rules, dynamic mechanics, large number of components, unique art, and exciting scenarios! Win in a world of senseless cruelty and causeless violence, crowded with hordes of zombies and crazy gangs in the board game about the zombie apocalypse Z-Game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
